de.tub.reader.model
Class UserReader

java.lang.Object
  de.tub.observer.Subject
      de.tub.reader.model.UserReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
IReader, IUserReader, Cloneable
public class UserReader
extends Subject
implements IUserReader, Cloneable

This reader reads user resources from a database and delegates the processing of each user to the given processor. A valid connection to the database is necessary.

This reader informs its observers after finishing each user resource with the UserFinished interest.

Author:
Sebastian Oelke
